lead_paragraph: James Harden recorded his seventh triple-double of the season while Montrezl Harrell scored a career-high 29 points off the bench to fuel the Houston Rockets' 140-116 win over the Los Angeles Clippers on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Harden, Harrell Ignite Rockets in Rout of Clippers
